### Solution:

```java
public class Solution {
    public String decode(String s) {
        StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();
        String[] words = s.split(" ");
        for (String word: words) {
            sb.append(word.replace("+", " "));
        }
        return sb.toString();
    }
}
```

